      Rule 3 - Conditional Field Rule (the polymorphic invariant):
        With party_type=Organization, the UI Policy mandates:
          * <organization> populated with a core_company reference
            (DONE BELOW: "Synthetic Org Alpha" resolved by name lookup)
          * <person> empty  (DONE BELOW: empty <person/> element)
        The inverse pattern is exercised by parties 01, 03, 04, 06,
        and 08 (party_type=Person, person populated, organization
        empty). This file establishes the canonical Organization-
        branch invariant on the Complaint flow's In Progress case.

      Rule 4 - Reference resolution by stable human-readable key (AAP
              Section 0.7.2 "NO sys_id literals anywhere"):
        case         : <case display_value="CASE0000008">CASE0000008</case>
