                       idempotent number lookup. CASE0000008 is the
                       auto-numbered value the platform generates for
                       demo case 08 since cases 01 through 08 import
                       in order with the CASE0000001-format auto-number
                       counter (case 01 -> CASE0000001, case 02 ->
                       CASE0000002, ..., case 08 -> CASE0000008). This
                       party's parent therefore resolves to the demo
                       case 08 record at
                       ../cases/x_casemgmt_case_demo_08.xml.
        organization : <organization display_value="Synthetic Org Alpha"
